| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3509 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 08437dac-c1e9-5ce8-81cb-3bc9f27c38c4"
